review.comments: Best host ever! We had a horrible schedule due to flight delays at JFK because of the weather and they accommodated our needs! Like really went above and beyond to work with our schedule. Amazing host! The apartment is great too,  very spacious! And only 1 flight up! That beats all the other places we checked out around the area. The location is what makes this apartment truly satisfactory! Less than 2 min walk from all the major subway lines, all the best eating places in my opinion! Me and my husband love ramen and the apartment is a 5 min walk to totto and ippudo ramen! I can't say anything bad about this place because there's none! Thank you letty and Karl for allowing us to stay here and have a wonderful experience!
